      • JobHolder

        public JobHolder(java.lang.Long id,
         int priority,
         java.lang.String groupId,
         int runCount,
         Job job,
         long createdNs,
         long delayUntilNs,
         long runningSessionId)
        Parameters:
        id - Unique ID for the job. Should be unique per queue
        priority - Higher is better
        groupId - which group does this job belong to? default null
        runCount - Incremented each time job is fetched to run, initial value should be 0
        job - Actual job to run
        createdNs - System.nanotime
        delayUntilNs - System.nanotime value where job can be run the very first time
        runningSessionId -
